"translation":"তারাই হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_018_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20476,"position":22,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/009_018_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20477,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلْمُهْتَدِينَ","translation":"সঠিক পথপ্রাপ্তদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_018_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20478,"position":24,"arabic":"١٨","translation":"(১৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":19,"arabic":"۞ أَجَعَلْتُمْ سِقَايَةَ ٱلْحَآجِّ وَعِمَارَةَ ٱلْمَسْجِدِ ٱلْحَرَامِ كَمَنْ ءَامَنَ بِٱللَّهِ وَٱلْيَوْمِ ٱلْءَاخِرِ وَجَٰهَدَ فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ ۚ لَا يَسْتَوُۥنَ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ لَا يَهْدِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"Do you, perchance, regard the [mere] giving of water to pilgrims and the tending of the Inviolable House of Worship as being equal to [the works of] one who believes in God and the Last Day and strives hard in God's cause? These [things] are not equal in the sight of God. And God does not grace with His guidance people who [deliberately] do wrong.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1254.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":21545,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ أَجَعَلْتُمْ","translation":"কি তোমরা মনে করেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_019_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21546,"position":2,"arabic":"سِقَايَةَ","translation":"পানি পান করানো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_019_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21547,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْحَآجِّ","translation":"হাজ্বীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_019_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21548,"position":4,"arabic":"وَعِمَارَةَ","translation":"ও রক্ষণাবেক্ষণ করা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_019_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21549,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمَسْجِدِ","translation":"মাসজিদে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_019_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21550,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْحَرَامِ","translation":"হারামের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_019_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21551,"position":7,"arabic":"كَ